description: Version control standards for template repository
globs:
alwaysApply: agent
---

- Use conventional commit format: `feat(scope):`, `fix(scope):`, `docs(scope):`.
- Scope should indicate template type: `repo`, `monorepo`, `root`.
- Example: `feat(repo): add TypeScript configuration template`.
- Update README.md placeholder table when adding new placeholders.
